Package: STRbaseclient
Title: Access NIST's STRbase API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Maarten", "Kruijver", , "maarten.kruijver@esr.cri.nz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6890-7632"))
Description: NIST's STRBase hosts STR-related information for the human identity community. Data can be browsed through "https://strbase.nist.gov/". This client accesses the API directly.  
